      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need help drafting a formal disciplinary email. I have an employee who has been consistently about 15 minutes late to their shifts every day for the last two weeks. I need the tone to be professional and firm, but not overly aggressive. Just a standard first warning for punctuality issues.",
