      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Notice of Punctuality Concerns and Formal Warning\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has come to my attention regarding your punctuality. As you are aware, our company values punctuality and consistency, and it has been noted that you have been arriving approximately 15 minutes late to your shifts over the past two weeks.\n\nWhile I understand that unforeseen circumstances can sometimes cause delays, it is essential to maintain a professional standard of punctuality. Your tardiness not only disrupts your own workflow but also impacts the rest of the team and the overall logistics of our operations. When team members are not punctual, it can lead to a domino effect, causing delays and inefficiencies that affect everyone.\n\nAs a first warning, I kindly request that you make a concerted effort to arrive on time for your shifts moving forward. Failure to do so may result in further disciplinary action.\n\nThank you for your attention to this matter. I trust that you will take this warning seriously and make the necessary adjustments to your schedule.\n\nSincerely,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]",
      "source": "target",
